o","count":1,"users":["U8R597E9H"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"DAGs"}]},{"client_msg_id":"16bf26bf-0f41-4b29-87b3-19be9169f4a9","type":"message","user":"UKHUVMBJR","text":"うちのプロデューサーの話ですが、毎週の定例で交流を深めたりゲームについてより考えるためのワークショップをしたりとか","ts":"1606186787.111300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"UMaV"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1e93d8ae-ea0a-47a2-8baf-04891a3fa29f","type":"message","user":"U7B4ZD49X","text":"うちは特にこれといってしてないですね。。。","ts":"1606186364.110800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"K5/5D"}]},{"client_msg_id":"cc7dbcd9-4a11-404b-a164-2675c1a8db80","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"日々の業務中のコミュニケーションとかなにか工夫したりされてますか？","ts":"1606185645.110100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"gc1eG"}]},{"client_msg_id":"856495e7-8bde-4e8b-aba9-c08034954a96","type":"message","user":"UKHUVMBJR","text":"うちだと継承するには対話で熱量を伝えるのが必要でしょうという話なので、\n新しいチームに入ったメンバーがいたら最低限出社して伝えるべきことは伝えよう的な感じにしてますね","ts":"1606185586.109500","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"naruhodo","count":1,"users":["U7B4ZD49X"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"9Vu"}]},{"client_msg_id":"61805832-7e29-470b-83fd-e54b836b8a6a","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"テレワークが前提になって、この「継承する」にもちゃんと仕組みがないとなぁと思っている。(いや、いままでもそうだったんだろうが、よりその傾向にある、というか)","ts":"1606184620.108700","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"wakaru","count":1,"users":["U7B4ZD49X"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"duoX"}]},{"client_msg_id":"6360c3df-76e0-45aa-869f-f24212fc802b","type":"message","user":"U7B4ZD49X","text":"継承しようにもみんながKoRoNさんやmattnさんみたいになれるわけでもないからなー。。。\nやってる時間も密度も違う。\n仕組みで作り出せるレベルには限度がある。突き抜ける人が現れるといいけど。","ts":"1606184392.107000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"rap"}]},{"client_msg_id":"dacc6f05-08a7-48bb-8070-477939d615fd","type":"message","user":"UKHUVMBJR","text":"責任感についてはそういう、遊ぶ人のことちゃんと考えてるか？みたいな文化の面で後押しされてる感じですね","ts":"1606184243.105000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"rlPK"}]},{"client_msg_id":"82509f51-8f4b-43af-bd0c-1e12dbf8ad7b","type":"message","user":"UKHUVMBJR","text":"ゲーム作ってると非属人化と効率化は全力で進めた上で、個人がちゃんと考えられることが求められるので\nそこで違和感はあんま感じないですね","ts":"1606184217.104000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Rz+cQ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"ee0d19bc-584d-4dd5-9964-3aff13e08054","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"うまいこと言語化できてない部分なので、あんまり大口たたけないｗ","ts":"1606184080.101700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"apj"}]},{"client_msg_id":"d3d07aa5-7d90-493d-be6c-26e1c9355887","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"本当にコモディティ化している作業なのか、創造的に考えてやらないといけない作業なのか。","ts":"1606184046.101000","edited":{"user":"U8R597E9H","ts":"1606184117.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"f7m"}]},{"client_msg_id":"07c43e07-302b-4670-adea-427cffd661d6","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"線引きは難しいんですよね。メンバから「これをチェックシートやドキュメントにまとめて誰でもできるようにしたほうがいい」という言説が出ることがあるが","ts":"1606184006.100300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"R4zC"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7e07582a-d026-40a0-bd1c-4038157b8e00","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"なので「この人しかできない」オンリーワンを組織でバックアップして、のちに組織で担えるように整えてくのがビジネスなのかなと。","ts":"1606183966.099500","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"tomyo","count":1,"users":["U03C4RC8X"]},{"name":"wakaru","count":2,"users":["U7B4ZD49X","U8R597E9H"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"KrH4H"}]},{"client_msg_id":"0761c09e-1cd1-4316-b6c1-95526ce72fd7","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"極論、誰でもできる仕事はビジネスにならんのですよ。スケールメリットなレッドオーシャンなビジネスくらいにしか。","ts":"1606183881.097900","edited":{"user":"U06BRP8VD","ts":"1606183889.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ew4"}]},{"client_msg_id":"80505691-a342-4226-a790-7102345b6051","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"なんでそんなピンポイントな絵文字があるんだｗｗｗ","ts":"1606183871.097600","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"fufufu","count":1,"users":["U03C4RC8X"]},{"name":"sorena","count":1,"users":["U013QL1RAPN"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"V/I"}]},{"client_msg_id":"d73febe2-dc2c-4f45-83b9-e71b525aede1","type":"message","user":"U03C4RC8X","text":":keishou-chance:","ts":"1606183857.097000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"p8A"}]},{"client_msg_id":"6a660d41-b589-4211-a6b4-e7c7cc7387a8","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"ので、おそらく「誰かが突き抜ける」→「それを継承する方法がある」が正しいんだろうなって思います。なるほど。","ts":"1606183832.096700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"gx/"}]},{"client_msg_id":"6a0326e0-6593-4aa5-b272-0eacebd59cbc","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"「誰でもできる仕組みにする」と言われると、正しい気がしてしまうが。誰でもできるような仕事をやってるんだったか？という気持ちが出てきてしまう。","ts":"1606183812.096100","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"wakaru","count":1,"users":["U7B4ZD49X"]},{"name":"java","count":1,"users":["U03C4RC8X"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zwhM"}]},{"client_msg_id":"e3db068c-0c2e-44fb-8c3d-98e33f38a223","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"とてもわかります。","ts":"1606183781.095500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,